jokeText: Why was the math book sad? Because it had too many problems
What do you call cheese that isn't yours? Nacho Cheese!
Why couldn't the bicycle stand up by itself? It was two-tired!
Why did the tomato turn red? Because it saw the salad dressing!
I wanted another piece of pizza... but she said I could only have ONE PIECE
Why was the computer cold? It left its windows open!
How do you make a tissue dance? Put a little BOOGIE in it!
Why did the cookie go to the doctor? Because it felt crummy...
I just realized why I can't tell an egg a joke... they might crack.
Two skeletons can't fight because neither one of them have the guts. HAHAHAHA
